--- In neat@yahoogroups.com, "Kenneth Stanley" <kstanley@c...> wrote:
> Risto Miikkulainen and I got interviewed today by local television 
> channel KXAN, mostly about NERO.  The broadcast was on channel 36 here 
> at 4pm today.  In case you are curious about what we're like in 
> person, or NERO (which is coming soon), here is a link with a video 
> clip (click on the little camera icon):
> 
> http://www.kxan.com/Global/story.asp?S=3381601&nav=0s3caC93

Well done Ken!  It's interesting to finally be able to put a voice and
some mannerisms to that picture of yours on your homepage.

> Keep in mind there was an hour-and-a-half interview spliced into 3 
> minutes of soundbites...so it's not exactly the way we said things.  
> However, all things considered, it's not bad.

Would be nice if they let you edit it yourself, but that's probably
not too realistic for every news story that they do.

Mike
